title: 游戏崩溃以及BUG
author: sky丿天谴
txt_content:

replies.author: 结城希亚
replies.txt_content:
https://c-t.work/s/2d9b85ebccd840
卸载原来java，装上这里的java
把你mods替换到这里的客户端
分配4096内存再启动就行

replies.txt_content:
